value: Breeds: Cape Verde Is, Desertas (Madeira); visitor, sea: near West Africa coast.
Cape Verde and Desertas islands; ranges e Atlantic Ocean
Breeds on the Cape Verde Islands (Santo Antao, Sao Nicolau, Fogo, Sao Tiago), and on Bugio, Desertas Islands, off Madeira. Not distinguishable at sea from madeira.
